<article class="teaser teaser-lg blog-entry--teaser" data-nid="5019520">

  <div class="teaser-lg--main">

          <div class="teaser-lg__image">
        
              <a href="/us/blog/play-your-way-sane/202405/putting-the-kids-in-charge"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_1_1_288x288/public/teaser_image/blog_entry/2024-05/patrick-buck-iPpy3Mupk8k-unsplash.jpg?itok=wsGkHMNK" width="288" height="288" alt="" title="Patrick Buck / Unsplash" />

</a>

      
      </div>
    
    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/play-your-way-sane/202405/putting-the-kids-in-charge" rel="bookmark">Putting the Kids in Charge</a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            The kids are all right... as long as we give them the space and opportunity to flex their independence. 
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            The kids are all right... as long as we give them the space and opportunity to flex their independence. 
      </p>
  </article>
</div>
    <div class="teaser-listing-item">




<article class="teaser teaser-lg blog-entry--teaser" data-nid="5019497">

  <div class="teaser-lg--main">

          <div class="teaser-lg__image">
          <a href="/us/blog/what-the-wild-things-are/202404/the-3-ps-perfectionism-procrastination-and-paralysis"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_1_1_288x288/public/field_blog_entry_images/2024-04/20240403_170950.jpg?itok=VED2VhAR" width="288" height="288" alt="" title="Samantha Stein" />

</a>

      </div>
    
    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/what-the-wild-things-are/202404/the-3-ps-perfectionism-procrastination-and-paralysis" rel="bookmark">The 3 Ps: Perfectionism, Procrastination, and Paralysis</a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            The 3 Ps can cause us to grind to a halt and fail to accomplish our goals. However, there are steps we can take to avoid this vicious cycle. 
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            The 3 Ps can cause us to grind to a halt and fail to accomplish our goals. However, there are steps we can take to avoid this vicious cycle. 
      </p>
  </article>
</div>
